	   <tr><td colspan=2>that is incorrect, dmg bonus is based on your lvl and the weapons dly a weapon with 50dly will have a larger dmg bonus than one with 40 dly, i know skill has nothing to do with it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Take 2 weps with the same dly(or at least the first digit is the same, a 41 and a 49dly wep have the same bonus) and one uses a skill you have maxed and one is a skill u have never touched.  The dmg bonus will be exactly the same for both.<br>&nbsp;<br>-Omnislayer Darktide<br>-Omnislayerr Darktide<br>&lt;Erud's Chosen&gt;<br>Knights of TZ<br></td></tr>
